\v 2 Zwanini lokhu\x + Hos. 5.1.\x*, badala\x + 1.14.\x*, libeke indlebe, lonke bahlali belizwe\x + 1.14.\x*. \add Kwake\add* kwenzeka lokhu yini ensukwini zenu, kumbe lensukwini zaboyihlo\x + 2.2.\x*?
\v 3 Landiselani abantwana benu ngakho, labantwana benu abantwana babo, labantwana babo esinye isizukulwana\x + Hlab. 78.4.\x*.
\v 4 Okutshiywe zintothoviyane\x + 2.25; Amos 4.9; Mal. 3.11.\x* isikhonyane sikudlile\x + Deut, 28.38; Eks. 10.4; Amos 7.1.\x*; lokutshiywe yisikhonyane\x + Deut, 28.38; Eks. 10.4; Amos 7.1.\x* iqhwagi likudlile\x + 2.25; Hlab. 78.46.\x*; lokutshiywe liqhwagi inswabanda ikudlile.
\p
\v 5 Phaphamani, zidakwa, likhale inyembezi, liqhinqe isililo\x + Isa. 24.11.\x*, lonke banathi bewayini, ngenxa yewayini elitsha\x + 3.18; Amos 9.13; Isa. 49.26.\x*, ngoba liqunyiwe lasuka emlonyeni wenu\x + Isa. 32.10.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba isizwe senyukele elizweni lami\x + 2.2.\x*, esilamandla, esingelanani\x + 2.2.\x*; amazinyo aso angamazinyo esilwane\x + Isam. 9.8.\x*, silamazinyo emihlathi\x + Jobe 29.17.\x* esilwane esisikazi\x + Jobe 4.11.\x*.
\v 7 Senze ivini lami laba yincithakalo, lesihlahla sami somkhiwa saba zimvava\x + 1.12.\x*; sakwebula lokukwebula, sakuphosela phansi, ingatsha zakho zaba mhlophe\x + Gen. 40.10,12.\x*.
