\v 8 Qhinqani isililo njengentombi emsulwa ebhinciswe isaka\x + 1.13; 1 Kho. 20.31.\x* ngenxa yomyeni wobutsha bayo\x + Zaga 2.17; Jer. 3.4.\x*.
\v 9 Umnikelo wokudla lomnikelo wokunathwayo uqunyiwe wasuka endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1.13,16; 2.14; Dan. 8.11,12.\x*. Abapristi\x + 1.13; 2.17; Isa. 61.6; Hez. 45.4.\x*, izikhonzi zeN\nd kosi\nd*, bayalila\x + 1.13; 2.17; Isa. 61.6; Hez. 45.4.\x*.
\v 10 Insimu ichithiwe, umhlabathi uyalila\x + Hos. 4.3.\x*; ngoba amabele achithiwe\x + 2.19,24; Hos. 2.8.\x*, iwayini elitsha\x + 2.19,24;Hos. 2.8.\x*\x + Isa. 24.7.\x* lomile\x + 1.12,17; Josh. 2.10; 4.23; Hos. 13.15.\x*, amafutha\x + 2.19,24; Hos. 2.8.\x* aphela amandla\x + Isa. 16.8.\x*.
