\v 11 Banini lenhloni, balimi, qhinqani isililo, baphathizivini\x + Jer. 14.4 .\x*, ngenxa yengqoloyi langenxa \w yebhali\w**; ngoba isivuno sensimu sichithekile.
\v 12 Ivini libunile\x + 1.12,17; Josh. 2.10; 4.23; Hos. 13.15.\x*, lomkhiwa uphele amandla\x + 1.12.\x*; \w ipomegranati\w**, lesihlahla selala\x + Hlab. 92.12.\x*, lesihlahla se-aphula\x + Zaga 25.11.\x*, zonke izihlahla zeganga zomile, ngoba intokozo\x + Isa. 24.11; Jer. 48.33.\x* ibunile yasuka ebantwaneni babantu\x + 1.12,17; Josh. 2.10; 4.23; Hos. 13.15.\x*.
