\v 13 Bhincani\x + Jer. 4.8; Mika 1. 8.\x*\x + 1.8.\x*, lilile, bapristi\x + Jer. 4.8; Mika 1. 8.\x*, qhinqani isililo, zikhonzi zelathi\x + Jer. 4.8; Mika 1.8.\x*. Wozani, lilale ebusuku emasakeni\x + 1.8.\x*, zikhonzi zikaNkulunkulu wami\x + 1.9.\x*; ngoba umnikelo wokudla lomnikelo wokunathwayo kugodliwe endlini kaNkulunkulu wenu\x + 1.9.\x*.
