\v 14 Yehlukanisani ukuzila ukudla\x + 2.15,16; 2 Lan. 20.3; 2 Kho. 10.20.\x*, libize umhlangano onzulu\x + 2.15,16; 2 Lan. 20.3; 2 Kho. 10.20.\x*, libuthanise\x + 2.15,16; 2 Lan. 20.3; 2 Kho. 10.20.\x* abadala\x + 1.2.\x*, \add labo\add* bonke abahlali belizwe, \add e\add*ndl\add ini\add* yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 1.2.\x*, likhale eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 15 Maye ngalolosuku! Ngoba usuku lweN\nd kosi\nd* luseduze\x + Isa. 13.6; Isa. 13.9; Jer. 46.10; Hez. 30.3; Jow. 2.1; Jobe 24.1.\x*, luzafika njengencithakalo\x + Hos. 7.13.\x* evela kuSomandla\x + Hez. 1.24.\x*.
\v 16 Ukudla kakuqunywanga yini phambi kwamehlo ethu\x + 1.9.\x*, ukuthaba lentokozo\x + Dute. 12.6,7; 16.11,14,15.\x* kusuka endlini kaNkulunkulu wethu\x + 1.9.\x*?
\v 17 Inhlanyelo iyabola ngaphansi kwamagade ayo; izibuya zingamanxiwa, iziphala zidilizelwe phansi\x + Hagg. 2.19.\x*, ngoba amabele abunile\x + 1.12,17; Josh. 2.10; 4.23; Hos. 13.15.\x*.
\v 18 Yeka ukububula kwezifuyo\x + 1.20; Hos. 4.3; Jer. 12.4; Jow. 2.22; Jona 3.7; 4.11.\x*! Imihlambi yenkomo ididekile, ngoba kayilalo idlelo\x + Eks. 14.3.\x*; lemihlambi yezimvu iyahlupheka\x + Hos. 13.16.\x*.
