\v 19 Ngiyakhala kuwe\x + Hlab. 50.15.\x*, N\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba umlilo uqedile\x + 1.20.\x* amadlelo enkangala\x + Jer. 9.10.\x*, lelangabi lilumathise zonke izihlahla zeganga\x + 2.3.\x*.
\v 20 Lenyamazana zeganga\x + 1.20; Hos. 4.3; Jer. 12.4; Jow. 2.22; Jona 3.7; 4.11.\x* ziyakhala kuwe\x + Hlab. 42.1; Jobe 38.41; Hlab. 104.21; 145.15; 147.9.\x*, ngoba izifudlana zamanzi\x + Hlab. 18.15.\x* zitshile\x + 1 Kho. 17.7; 18.5.\x*, lomlilo uqede amadlelo enkangala\x + 1.20.\x*.